        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Iran Nuclear Deal Advice and Consent Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of federal funds to rejoin the Joint Comprehensive Plan of Action&#8212;commonly known as the Iran nuclear deal&#8212;unless the President commits to submit any successor agreement to the Senate for advice and consent as a treaty.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
